    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this absolute gem. It is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled right off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and there\u2019s not a single flaw to be found. It\u2019s super smooth to drive and ready for a new home. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 45900.0,
