    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a definitive analog driving machine. At its heart is the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Dual VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced to ensure optimal cam timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile, short-throw shifts, paired with a reinforced rear subframe to maintain rigid chassis integrity under lateral load. This example exhibits zero subframe cracking and has had the critical rod bearing service addressed with documented precision. The factory-spec limited-slip differential remains tight, and the suspension retains its original kinematic excellence with fresh OEM bushings and dampers. The exterior finish maintains a deep luster with consistent micrometer readings across all panels, and the interior's Nappa leather remains supple and free of bolster wear. A mechanically peerless specimen for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
